Usage: chpl [flags] [source files]

Compilation Trace Options:
      --print-commands                   Print system commands
      --print-passes                     Print compiler passes

Code Size Options:
      --count-tokens                     Count tokens
      --print-code-size                  Print code size statistics

Parallelism Control Options:
      --[no-]local                       Constrain execution to one locale
      --[no-]serial                      Serialize parallel concepts

Optimization Control Options:
      --baseline                         Disable almost all optimizations
      --fast                             Use fast default settings
      --[no-]ieee-float                  Enable non-ieee compliant
                                         optimizations
      --no-copy-propagation              Disable copy propagation
      --no-expand-iterators-inline-opt   Disable the expansion of iterators
                                         inlined around loop bodies
      --no-flow-analysis                 Disable optimizations requiring flow
                                         analysis
      --no-inline                        Do not inline functions
      --no-single-loop-iterator-opt      Disable the optimization of iterators
                                         composed of a single loop

Run-time Semantic Check Options:
      --no-checks                        Disable all following checks
      --[no-]bounds-checks               Disable bounds checking
      --[no-]nil-checks                  Disable nil checking

C Code Generation Options:
      --[no-]cpp-lines                   Generate #line annotations
      --savec <directory>                Save generated C code in directory
      --short-names                      Use short names

C Code Compilation Options:
      --ccflags <flags>                  Back-end C compiler flags
      --ldflags <flags>                  Back-end C linker flags
  -l, --lib-linkage <library>            C library linkage
  -L, --lib-search-path <directory>      C library search path
      --make <make utility>              Make utility for generated code
  -g, --[no-]debug                       Allow debugging of generated C code
  -O, --[no-]optimize                    Optimize generated C code
  -o, --output <filename>                Name output executable

Miscellaneous Options:
      --chplhome <directory>             Over-ride $CHPL_HOME
      --[no-]devel                       Compile as developer
      --explain-call <call>[:<module>][:<line>]
                                         Explain resolution of call
      --instantiate-max <max>            Limit number of instantiations
      --main-module <module>             Specify module where main is located
      --no-warnings                      Disable output of warnings
  -s, --set <name>[=<value>]             Set config param value

Compiler Information Options:
      --copyright                        Show copyright
  -h, --help                             Help (show this list)
      --help-env                         Environment variable help
      --help-settings                    Current flag settings
      --license                          Show license
      --version                          Show version
